            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " — to complicate the GOP’s plans while Republican senators are either campaigning for reelection or under COVID quarantine (",
            "type": "text",
